- Character creation stats: 
	- Stat Array
		- 15, 14, 13,12,10, 8
	- Default Point Buy Rules
		Available Points - 27
		Maximum Attribute Before Racial Bonus - 15
		Minimum Attribute Before Racial Bonus - 8
	- 4d6, discard one dice to build pool, then assign.
- Each character will get ability improvements for every 4 character levels, still able to subsititue a feat
- Each chacter will get a feat for every 5 character levels
- Inspiriation is given for chacter defining rp moments
- Quaffing a potion will be a bonus action
